'''1,2-二(二溴甲基)苯'''是一种[[有机化合物|有机化合物]]，化学式为C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>4</sub>(CHBr<sub>2</sub>)<sub>2</sub>。它的三种二溴甲基[[同分异构体|同分异构体]]都存在，但邻位的异构体是研究最多的。它可由[[邻二甲苯|邻二甲苯]]和溴的光化学反应制得。<ref name=OS>{{cite journal |doi=10.15227/orgsyn.034.0082|title=o-Phthalaldehyde|journal=Organic Syntheses|year=1954|first1=J. C.|last1=Bill|first2=D. S.|last2=Tarbell |volume=34|page=82}}</ref>
:C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>4</sub>(CH<sub>3</sub>)<sub>2</sub>  +  4 Br<sub>2</sub>  →  C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>4</sub>(CHBr<sub>2</sub>)<sub>2</sub>  +  4 HBr

它可以和[[碘化钠|碘化钠]]反应，生成α,α'-二溴邻二(亚甲基)苯，在捕获剂的存在下和亲双烯体反应生成亚萘基化合物<!-- 原文为 naphthylene -->。如果没有捕获剂，则得到α,α'-二溴苯并环丁烷：<ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.1021/ja01533a032|title=Condensed Cyclobutane Aromatic Compounds. VIII. The Mechanism of Formation of 1,2-Dibromobenzocyclobutene; A New Diels-Alder Synthesis|year=1959|last1=Cava|first1=M. P.|last2=Deana|first2=A. A.|last3=Muth|first3=K.|journal=Journal of the American Chemical Society|volume=81|issue=24|pages=6458–6460}}</ref>
:C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>4</sub>(CHBr<sub>2</sub>)<sub>2</sub>  +  2 NaI → C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>4</sub>(=CHBr)<sub>2</sub>  +  2 NaBr  +  I<sub>2</sub>
:C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>4</sub>(=CHBr)<sub>2</sub> → C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>4</sub>(CHBr)<sub>2</sub>

这些二亚甲基苯的环加成反应可以得到[[并苯|并苯]]。<ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.1055/s-1986-31603|title=An Efficient Synthetic Strategy for Naphthalene Annellation of Norbornenylogous Systems|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_synthesis_1986-04_4/page/328|year=1986|last1=Paddon-Row|first1=Michael N.|last2=Patney|first2=Harish K.|journal=Synthesis|volume=1986|issue=4|pages=328–330}}</ref>

